Package it.polimi.ingsw.core.model

Class ModelView

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.core.model.ModelView
public class ModelView extends Object
This class represents a ModelView in the game. It maintains the game state, player states, and other game-related data.

      side - The side of the card to be set. True for front side, false for back side.
